# 🚀 TaskBlast - To-Do List App

Turn Your Day into a ToDo Adventure! ✅

TaskBlast is a simple and intuitive To-Do List app built with React. It allows you to manage your tasks efficiently and stay organized throughout the day. With TaskBlast, you can:

## Key Features

✅ Add new tasks with ease.
❌ Remove tasks you no longer need.
✅ Mark tasks as completed.
✅ Enjoy a clean and user-friendly interface.

## Getting Started

Follow these steps to get TaskBlast up and running on your local machine:

1. Clone this repository to your local environment.
2. Install the necessary dependencies using `npm install`.
3. Start the development server with `npm start`.
4. Open the app in your web browser.

## Usage

- Enter a task in the input field and click "NEW" to add it to your to-do list.
- Click "Delete" next to a task to remove it from the list.
- Click a task to mark it as completed.

Stay organized and accomplish your tasks with TaskBlast! 📅

## Technologies Used

- React
- JavaScript
- HTML
- CSS

